    dc:description "Figure 5. Colobomatus gymnocranii sp. nov., adult female. (A) Habitus, ventral; (B) antennule, ventral; (C) buccal capsule and mouthparts, ventral; (D) leg 1, ventrolateral; (E) leg 2, ventrolateral; (F) leg 3, ventrolateral; (G) tip of anterior thoracic process, ventral. Abbreviations: A, antenna; la, labium; mx, maxillule; Mx, maxilla." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4632031/files/figure.png" ;
